name: Jaydes
description: '''Jayden Yen Dumont''' (born February 24, 2006) known professionally as '''Jaydes''' (previously known as '''Evvls'''), is an American rapper, singer, producer, and songwriter from [[Tamarac, Florida]]. He gained popularity in the [[underground hip-hop]] scene in 2022 from [[social media]] and [[Music streaming service|streaming platforms]] such as [[SoundCloud]]. His song Rose, gained substantial virality on [[TikTok]].
